ec_members.name: Arafat Ahmed Sajib
ec_members.biography: Arafat Ahmed Sajib is a dedicated and active member of the Mymensingh Students' Association, SUST. As the President of the 15th Executive Committee, he has shown exemplary leadership and commitment to the association's mission and goals. He is currently in his 4th year studying Chemistry at SUST, where he continues to excel both academically and in his extracurricular activities.
